            "__cdata": "<p class=\"p_20\">21. The patient presented with body aches and pains with anorexia. She is menopausal for the last 2 years. Labs show: low 25 (OH) vitD, low serum Calcium, low Phosphates, low 24-hour urinary Calcium and increased Alkaline Phosphatase. X-ray Hip shows a fracture of the right side. What is your diagnosis?</p>"
