            "__cdata": "<p class=\"p_20\">58. A 6-month-old boy is found to have bilateral metaphyseal fractures of both proximal and distal ends of the tibia. The mother says that her boyfriend takes care of the infant while she is at work. Her boyfriend explains the injuries as the result of multiple falls from bed. Which of the following is the most likely diagnosis?</p>"
